{"tid":2168012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"整手工材料地方一問","createTime":"2020-08-21T12:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T03:06:23.000Z","uid":244569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ce64e657473fe7c32498df3c785274d34926cb","tid":2168012,"uid":244569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"喺屋企好悶，想試下整手工，但耳環同布藝既材料都唔知邊度買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問過整手工既朋友材料喺邊度買，結果佢同我講<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">佢喺淘寶買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n罷左淘寶好耐，想爭氣啲喺香港買材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想請問有無人知道邊度可以買整耳環既材料 仲有香港邊度可以買拉鍊嗰啲材料（我知道深水埗賣開布藝，但之前去搵唔到邊間有得賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315f7fc14ddf38e4140de472e29cf3a296ce32be","tid":2168012,"uid":20117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:59:13.000Z","msg":"去ssp汝州街,有布有飾件配件員買，去買布唔好太夜去，排檔比較早收，入夜好雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5314ea8ce6718dd318e516f541fdc7a5af03a4b","tid":2168012,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"買布, 拉鏈可以去西九龍中心隔離果個栅仔, 應該仲未執<br />\n配料可以去汝州街一帶"},{"pid":"b04a35a58525111c7488e0cd02f5ee0c39111fe6","tid":2168012,"uid":244569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"315f7fc14ddf38e4140de472e29cf3a296ce32be","tid":2168012,"uid":20117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:59:13.000Z","msg":"去ssp汝州街,有布有飾件配件員買，去買布唔好太夜去，排檔比較早收，入夜好雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"之前去過汝州街，但好似唔見有得買